original_title: Call Me Back: The Uncommon Wisdom of Yvette Slosch
overview: Infamous NYC talent agent is determined to make a star out of her newest client, jazz violinist, Aaron Weinstein. She refuses to let Aaron's lack of name recognition, jazz's dwindling fan base, or the global pandemic get in her way.
title: Call Me Back: The Uncommon Wisdom of Yvette Slosch
